INSERT INTO `fdc_article` VALUES ('6', '9', 'yingdizichan', '【迪拜生活】在迪拜，买房好还是租房好？', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">基本上对所有阿联酋外籍来说，房租都是每个人每个月最大的一笔开支，一些迪拜居民表示，他们至少有40%的收入都用来支付房租了。</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">在迪拜，租一间一居室大概需要每年5万到9万迪拉姆，不同地段相差会很大。</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">近年来，迪拜大部分地区的租金也一直呈现下跌趋势。</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">那么现在在阿联酋买房到底值得吗？海湾新闻认为，如果你打算在阿联酋待超过15年，那么买房可能会比租房划算。而且实际上，大多数人待在阿联酋的时间都比他们最初预计的要长。</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><strong style=\"padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">买房好还是租房好？</span></strong><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">为了进行比较，我们使用Al Jafiliya地区附近的一套一居室来作为案例研究。根据RERA租赁增长指数，我们假设这套房子的出租价格为每年65,000迪拉姆，而购买一套这样的期房的价格为130万迪拉姆。</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/><span style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: 700; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">一次性费用</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); -ms-word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></p><table width=\"469\"><tbody style=\"padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><tr class=\"firstRow\" style=\"padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><td width=\"142\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: none; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: center; clear: both; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">项目</span></p></td><td width=\"215\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid solid solid none; padding: 0px 7px; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" colspan=\"2\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: center; clear: both; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">金额（<span style=\"padding: 0px; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: